{"tid":375421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門d垃圾出埋解放軍都仲係清唔走，點解？","createTime":"2017-08-26T13:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T14:45:24.000Z","uid":12599,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef3b18523b5300f8f61dcce95a17723f0ecf3df","tid":375421,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z8e1lo0d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz8e1lo0d&h=6c0d1e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6dzl4fgq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6dzl4fgq&h=74ecdabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xz83rabh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxz83rabh&h=6af87479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bk0ynudx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbk0ynudx&h=0a286ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nd人唔將垃圾放入垃圾袋，見有垃圾堆就隨手丢，結果大量散修修嘅垃圾，執都有排執<br />\n<br />\n有人乘機將唔要嘅大型垃圾就咁丢係路中心，應該自己搬去垃圾收集站先集中處理到<br />\n<br />\n有商鋪就咁將廢貨丢係路中心，仲有d過份到係濕水棉被<br />\n<br />\n有d商户pack 好廢貨但d人拆開曬來睇有無野執<br />\n<br />\n結論係: 公民教育低下，成日話天災香港無事就講風涼話，但你睇下澳門人自己係度做緊乜？"},{"pid":"93794ebd4b12a42a27bc248269f10cff618ea5e3","tid":375421,"uid":29606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d979baff83e4b568d7acc3af0dc8395545bdd332","tid":375421,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"支那蝗"},{"pid":"22990a87962807d26350a64424362eac7d38f8f7","tid":375421,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}